&FORCE_EVAL
  METHOD Quickstep
  &DFT
    &QS
      METHOD MNDO
      &SE
        INTEGRAL_SCREENING KDSO-D
        PERIODIC EWALD
        &COULOMB
          CUTOFF   [angstrom]     8.0
          RC_RANGE [angstrom]     0.1
        &END
        &SCREENING
          RC_TAPER [angstrom]     6.0
          RC_RANGE [angstrom]     0.1
